import React from 'react'
import Navigation from "../Navigation"
import SinglePage7Data from "../Img-Single-Page/SinglePage7Data"
import PortfContact from '../All_pages/PortfContact'
import Footer from "../Footer"


const SinglePage9 = () => {
     return (
          <>
                 <Navigation />
               <SinglePage7Data />
               <PortfContact />
               <Footer />
          </>
     )
}

export default SinglePage9
